author: adrianc
msg: Rewrite ModelFormField.java and related classes. Most of this is thread-safe now. Implemented a builder design because the original ModelForm design makes several passes over the fields - modifying them incrementally. Now ModelForm modifies builders instead, then when the parsing process is complete, the builders create the thread-safe field models.
